dct_title_s: Automobile roads from Los Angeles to Bakersfield via Tejon and Tehachapi Passes
dct_description_sm: Automobile Club of Southern California ; E.J.B.
Relief shown by hachures and spot shading (for desert).
Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Indicates distances from Los Angeles, San Francisco, and Bakersfield.
Numbered 1 in top right corner and 32 in bottom margin.
Belongs to a series of strip maps showing roads in California.
